 eeply rooted in Filipino culture and Midwestern sensibility. After early k
 itchen training in Detroit\, studying at the Culinary Institute of America
 \, and cooking in Chicago and Europe\, he relocated to Portland in 2014 an
 d opened his acclaimed Filipino restaurant\, Magna Kusina\, in 2019. His a
 ccolades include being named one of Food &amp\; Wine’s Best New Chefs of
